---
title: Gateway (CH) Internal Processing
---
flowchart TD
    RECV["📥 Receive MQTT-SN Packet<br/>(UDP Port 1883)"] --> PARSE["🔍 Parse Header<br/>Extract: MsgType, TopicID,<br/>MsgID, QoS, Emergency"]

    PARSE --> CHECK{Message Type?}

    CHECK -->|CONNECT| CONN["📋 Record Connection<br/>stats.connects++"]
    CONN --> ACK["📤 Send CONNACK"]

    CHECK -->|PUBLISH| PUB["📊 Update Stats<br/>topicCounts[topicId]++<br/>priorityCounts[priority]++"]
    
    PUB --> EMCHECK{Emergency?}
    EMCHECK -->|Yes| EMLOG["🚨 stats.emergencies++<br/>Log: EMERGENCY ALERT!"]
    EMCHECK -->|No| QUEUE

    EMLOG --> QUEUE["📥 Add to Priority Queue<br/>PriorityPacket {<br/>  priority, topicId,<br/>  msgId, rxTime<br/>}"]

    QUEUE --> QOSCHECK{QoS > 0?}
    QOSCHECK -->|Yes| PUBACK["📤 Send PUBACK<br/>(ECG and HR get confirmation)"]
    QOSCHECK -->|No| PROCESS
    PUBACK --> PROCESS

    PROCESS["⚡ ProcessQueue()"] --> QLOOP{Queue Empty?}

    QLOOP -->|No| TOP["📤 Get Top Priority Packet<br/>(highest priority first)"]
    TOP --> PCHECK{Priority Level?}
    PCHECK -->|3 CRITICAL| HIGH["🚨 processedHigh++<br/>Emergency processed!"]
    PCHECK -->|2 HIGH| HIGH2["🔴 processedHigh++<br/>ECG processed"]
    PCHECK -->|1 MEDIUM| MED["🔵 processedMed++<br/>HR processed"]
    PCHECK -->|0 LOW| LOW["🟢 processedLow++<br/>Temp processed"]

    HIGH --> QLOOP
    HIGH2 --> QLOOP
    MED --> QLOOP
    LOW --> QLOOP

    QLOOP -->|Yes| DONE["✅ All packets processed"]

    CHECK -->|DISCONNECT| DISC["📋 stats.disconnects++"]

    style RECV fill:#1F4E79,color:#fff
    style QUEUE fill:#AF52DE,color:#fff
    style PROCESS fill:#FF9500,color:#fff
    style HIGH fill:#C0392B,color:#fff
    style HIGH2 fill:#E74C3C,color:#fff
    style MED fill:#3498DB,color:#fff
    style LOW fill:#27AE60,color:#fff
    style EMLOG fill:#C0392B,color:#fff
